# Scratch stores + neutral/blind prose copies stay out (the experiment
# convention, R404 seeded-fixture rule). Tracked evidence = the manifest,
# the warm briefs, meridian-order.json, extractor-brief.md, the runbook,
# and report.md with the deterministic gate verdicts inlined. The warm prose
# (run/warm/story.md) and the reused compliance prose (run/compliance/story.md)
# ARE tracked as the graded deliverables (the R504 disclosure-report precedent:
# prose is tracked evidence, *.atomic.json scratch is not).
*.atomic.json
*.playthrough.json
run/labels/story-*.md
run/extract/story-*.md
# R525 exception: the typed fact base + dc-v2 plan IS a source (no tracked
# sections.json/facts.json reproduces it — it was reused from disclosure v2),
# and the deterministic reading-copy regeneration (report-playthrough-manuscript
# + `assemble --titles-from`) reads it for the per-world walk + canonical
# headings. Tracking it makes the six run/reading copies reproducible from
# tracked inputs alone (the track-the-source side of the R404 rule).
!authored.atomic.json
